0x90d93f5a390bfdbc401f92e916197ee17470a4.description: We are a pride of hackers, crypto-economists and open-source ideologues. We build technology to support freedom of the individual. Our values are centred on this pursuit entirely. We coordinate our own actions such that other network participants and governors can operate as efficiently as possible. We strive for the reduction of transaction costs within systems and the eradication of information asymmetries.
